{"tid":622643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"紅的失控衝九龍灣油站 卡喺行人隧道頂","createTime":"2018-04-09T09:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T17:06:11.000Z","uid":78632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3eceb6b7f426897058f889106b17223450ef6f7b","tid":622643,"uid":78632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/175400_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F175400_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=dd18a7e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/175408_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F175408_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f0603bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/175418_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F175418_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5159bf00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【16:45更新】紅的沿九龍灣宏展街行駛，疑轉入油站入氣時失控<br />\n<br />\n九龍灣下午發生驚險車禍！事發於下午約3時半，一部紅的沿九龍灣宏展街行駛，當駛至近MegaBox的中國石化油站附近，疑紅的準備轉入油站入氣，其間突然失控，撞毀油站入口的指示牌後，直衝向外面一條行人隧道，在撞毀鐵欄後，疑整架紅的飛起並卡在行人隧道頂的鐵欄，過程相當驚險，目前仍懸空在行人隧道上。69歲姓李的士司機一度被困，要由到場的消防員將他救出，他頭及胸口受傷，由救護車送往聯合醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n據途經現場的目擊者胡先生直言：「好驚訝！好似拍戲咁！」因他剛從附近一間戲院睇戲後離開，隨即看到如此震撼的畫面，令他大感驚訝。據他估計，的士衝過油站其間，一度撞毀油站的膠指示牌，幸而未有直衝入油站心臟地帶，否則後果不堪設想。胡先生笑言，的士穿過油站飛到行人隧道頂，未有直插入隧道內，加上相當亦有行人途經，真是不幸中的大幸。<br />\n<br />\n由於意外現場就在油站附近，消防擔心會發生炸爆或火警事故，遂拉喉以作戒備。此外，的士懸掛的位置相當棘手，警方現時將行人隧道及行人路封閉，正研究如何將的士吊回地面。<br />\n<br />\ndc9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb584f9dbde75ca546b1c8bebe5d45e020699bad","tid":622643,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"都幾難做到"},{"pid":"b945a4ec3446dc397de38a10c6c9b66d0a29f56d","tid":622643,"uid":61529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:56:41.000Z","msg":"新馬路三寶 的士狗 狗巴 休班警"},{"pid":"908c6bb973427d5741b310a7f1f4f2147a4d53b8","tid":622643,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:59:39.000Z","msg":"正常都撞爛鐵欄直插隧道, 點可以騎到上去? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130ba2a43e438c6aeeed67f7a3c5733277f24cd7","tid":622643,"uid":78632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"908c6bb973427d5741b310a7f1f4f2147a4d53b8","tid":622643,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:59:39.000Z","msg":"正常都撞爛鐵欄直插隧道, 點可以騎到上去? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T16:08:30.000Z","msg":"硬幣導致感應器嘅磁通量改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇phy佬解釋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"468b24afe2f8a1e75cc6a863a534abb56966add6","tid":622643,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b945a4ec3446dc397de38a10c6c9b66d0a29f56d","tid":622643,"uid":61529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T09:56:41.000Z","msg":"新馬路三寶 的士狗 狗巴 休班警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T17:06:11.000Z","msg":"係都小巴多過九巴啦<br />\n<br />\n成日沖燈屌人"}]}